Package Description
org.jnosql.aphrodite.antlr
This package contains the implementation of JNoSQL query using Antlr4.
org.jnosql.aphrodite.antlr.cache
This package contains the wrapper to the Antlr supplier implementation; this wrapper cache keeps the values converter to 5 minutes at least after that time the result will be expired.
org.jnosql.aphrodite.antlr.method  
org.jnosql.artemis
This package contains all comuns API to artemis.
org.jnosql.artemis.column
This package contains all objects to use a Column Family API.
org.jnosql.artemis.column.query
This package has the implementation to dynamic query to both Repository and RepositoryAsync on Column database.
org.jnosql.artemis.column.spi  
org.jnosql.artemis.configuration
This package has the classes to read configuration from file, json recommended, that is normally activated from ConfigurationUnit annotation.
org.jnosql.artemis.configuration.json  
org.jnosql.artemis.configuration.xml  
org.jnosql.artemis.configuration.yaml  
org.jnosql.artemis.document
This package contains all objects to use a Document Collection.
org.jnosql.artemis.document.query
This package has the implementation to dynamic query to both Repository and RepositoryAsync on document database.
org.jnosql.artemis.document.spi  
org.jnosql.artemis.graph
In computing, a graph database is a database that uses graph structures for semantic queries with nodes, edges and properties to represent and store data.
org.jnosql.artemis.graph.query
This package has the implementation to dynamic query to both Repository on Graph database.
org.jnosql.artemis.graph.spi  
org.jnosql.artemis.key

org.jnosql.artemis.key.query

org.jnosql.artemis.reflection
This package contains all reflections utils, the mapping of Field and class and also the extension to load all entity.
org.jnosql.artemis.util  
org.jnosql.artemis.validation
The artemis-validation is a subproject of Artemis that has the goals to validate the data using bean validation.
org.jnosql.diana.api
Diana is a flexible and extensible API to connect NoSQL databases.
org.jnosql.diana.api.column
This package contains all objects to use a Column Family API.
org.jnosql.diana.api.column.query
This package has the DSL domain to create both ColumnQuery and ColumnDeleteQuery
org.jnosql.diana.api.document
This package contains all objects to use a Document Collection.
org.jnosql.diana.api.document.query
This package has the DSL domain to create both DocumentQuery and DocumentDeleteQuery
org.jnosql.diana.api.key
This package contains all Key-value domain API.
org.jnosql.diana.api.key.query  
org.jnosql.diana.api.reader
The ValueReader has the goal read a information from Value by Class informed from Value.get(java.lang.Class).
org.jnosql.diana.api.writer
This package contains all ValueWriter supported by API by default.

This package domain has the representation of the query String in Classes.
